265
00:20:47,996 --> 00:20:49,163
Okay?

266
00:20:49,331 --> 00:20:51,165
How can I reach you?

267
00:20:51,833 --> 00:20:54,335
Just leave your number. I'll call you.

268
00:21:15,816 --> 00:21:16,857
YOUNG ELLIE:
Dad!

