274
00:21:38,213 --> 00:21:52,810
Dad?

275
00:22:02,946 --> 00:22:04,030
Daddy?

276
00:22:17,002 --> 00:22:26,427
Dad.

277
00:22:28,430 --> 00:22:30,348
