278
00:23:45,924 --> 00:23:47,591
Ellie.

279
00:23:49,177 --> 00:23:51,846
I know it's hard to understand this now...

280
00:23:52,848 --> 00:23:57,351
...but we aren't always meant to know
why things happen the way they do.

281
00:23:57,894 --> 00:24:02,231
Sometimes we just have to accept it
