00:41:46,420 --> 00:41:48,505
All right, it's restarting.

502
00:41:48,964 --> 00:41:50,715
Wait a minute. Those are numbers.

503
00:41:50,925 --> 00:41:54,010
That was a three,
the one before it was a two.

504
00:41:54,178 --> 00:41:57,597
Base-10 numbers. Just start counting now,
