552
00:44:53,649 --> 00:44:56,442
Mathematics is
the only truly universal language.

553
00:44:57,152 --> 00:44:59,737
It's no coincidence
that they're using primes.

554
00:44:59,947 --> 00:45:02,156
- I don't get it.
