564
00:45:34,732 --> 00:45:36,023
Let me first say that your...

565
00:45:36,191 --> 00:45:40,153
Actually, first, could you ask the gentlemen
with the firearms to wait outside?

566
00:45:40,320 --> 00:45:42,321
This is supposed to be a civilian facility.

567
00:45:48,787 --> 00:45:51,414
- Doctor, with all due respect to your...
