600
00:47:23,006 --> 00:47:24,173
WILLIE:
We're hot.

601
00:47:24,341 --> 00:47:27,426
Do me a favor, go get the blinds.
There is a lot of glare.

602
00:47:27,594 --> 00:47:29,095
You're patched in.

603
00:47:29,263 --> 00:47:33,432
All right, it's definitely an image.
Let's try and stabilize it.

