00:49:34,763 --> 00:49:37,473
Twenty million people died
defeating that son of a bitch...

628
00:49:37,641 --> 00:49:39,850
...and he's our first ambassador
to outer space?

629
00:49:40,018 --> 00:49:42,353
- Actually...
- The broadcast from the '36 Olympics...

630
00:49:42,521 --> 00:49:45,523
...was the first television transmission
