1518
01:54:35,118 --> 01:54:37,578
Steve, we're approaching our abort limits.

1519
01:54:39,956 --> 01:54:41,039
Okay to go.

1520
01:54:46,254 --> 01:54:47,462
I hear her!

1521
01:54:47,630 --> 01:54:50,465
I hear her. Barely, but she's there.

1522
01:54:50,633 --> 01:54:53,635
- Okay to go.
- She says she's okay to go.

1523
01:54:56,639 --> 01:54:58,765
Steve, we're real close.

1524
01:54:58,933 --> 01:55:01,810
- Electrical, reading in the core?
MAN: Internal environment normal.

1525
01:55:01,978 --> 01:55:04,980
Inside the core, the weather's beautiful.

1526
01:55:09,068 --> 01:55:10,319
I'm okay to go.

1527
01:55:10,820 --> 01:55:14,281
Okay to go. I'm okay to go.

